data.description: **This home qualifies for 0% down FHA loan+1.5% closing cost assistance through our partner lender & VA ASSUMABLE LOAN @ 4.25%.**  _______________________________________________________________________________________________________________   Beautiful 3/2 + Office/4th bedroom + 3 car garage with serene WATER VIEW on just under 1/4 acre lot with plenty of room for a pool in Riverview. Open floorplan with kitchen island, solid wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops and backsplash. Wood look plank tile in living, office and wet areas, carpet in bedrooms. The master suite includes trey ceilings with crown molding, dual vanities/sinks, large walk-in closet with built-in shelves tub and shower. Outside you'll find a peaceful water view in the retractable screened lanai along with many fruit and vegetable trees/plants. No grass to take care of either! Fully fenced yard. All appliances and outdoor TVs included. Located in Triple Creek community offering fantastic amenities with two pools, clubhouse, tennis courts, basketball court, fitness center, nature trails, playground and dog park. Dawson Elementary is located in the subdivision along with a daycare center. Close to shopping schools, HW 301 and I-75. **3-D Tour**https://www.zillow.com/view-imx/7f2cfb48-080f-4eda-8539-877ddb697833?initialViewType=pano&wl=true&setAttribution=mls
